<TITLE> PIO returns for 2 years </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, June 3 (bdnew24.com)  Former principal information officer (PIO) of the Press Information Department (PID) has been appointed to his previous post on contract. Harun-or-Rashid, the former PIO, was hired for two years. The establishment ministry in a statement issued Thursday announced the appointment. Current PIO of the information department, AKM Shamim Chowdhury, has been made additional PIO. Harun-or-Rashid served as PIO during the past 1996-2001 regime of the ruling Awami League government. bdn
